
                            ASK ARTHUR OUTLINE

Flow of app:
    1. Start Page
    2. Title Input
    3. Impact/Complexity Input
    4. Option Input
    5. Output type selection
    6. Results

General:
    3. Calculator object/script (all values go into this and creates object to display)

Impact/Complexity:
    1. Drop down input for Values

Option Input:
    1. Ability to dynamically add more than one Option
    2. Drop down for pro and con values

Output type selection:
    1. Buttons for each: "Jesus Take The Wheel!", "Show me Everything",
        "Based on Arthur's Calculations"

Results:
    1. Render each type based on output selection
    2. Api for graphs or library of sorts??

Extras:
    1. Animations
    2. Styling
    3. Chance for Arthur not to listen mini game
    4. Sounds: cat meow, hiss, and purr. Background music!


